The paper introduces a new sample complexity measure for empirical risk minimization and applies it to the problem of learning optimal auctions. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), game theory (cs.GT), economics and computation (cs.EC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
